data.description: Spacious 3 bedroom and 2-bathroom home located in an established neighborhood in Plant City close to Park Road. This is a block-concrete home, it has a 2-car carport and there is workshop for the Handyman in your life. House sits on an oversize lot (0.31 acres). The kitchen is very spacious and has an eat-in area for breakfast. You will love the walk-in closets and the spacious Main bedroom. Don’t wait to schedule a showing, book today before it is gone. Please note no showings before 12 Noon.
